nto a render prop that renders nothing except for children as a function of state and props. If you are really nice, you’ll allow this component to be both controlled and uncontrolled. Example: React Toggled.</p>\n<p>Opinion: Prefer Context and components over prop getters. Prop getters look gross with all the spreading. Or...you can expose both and tell me to shut up.</p>\n<pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js jsx\"><span class=\"keyword control js\"><span>import</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword operator js\"><span>*</span></span><span>&nbsp;as&nbsp;React&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword control js\"><span>from</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>react</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span><span class=\"punctuation terminator statement js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js jsx\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js jsx\"><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;comment</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js jsx\"><span class=\"meta export js\"><span class=\"keyword control js\"><span>export</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"variable language default js\"><span>default</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"meta class js\"><span class=\"storage type class js\"><span>class</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"entity name type class js\"><span>About</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"storage modifier js\"><span>extends</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"entity other inherited-class js\"><span>React</span></span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter propert